items.name: Cumulative DAUs
items.description: Shows the total cumulative number of unique users that have been using your app.

items.name: Users by browser (last 2 weeks)
items.description: Shows a breakdown of browsers used to visit your app per unique users in the last 14 days.

items.name: Repeat users over time
items.description: Shows you how many users visited your app for a specific number of days (e.g. a user that visited your app twice in the time period will be shown under "2 days").

items.name: Users by traffic source
items.derived_name: Retention of users based on doing Pageview for the first time and returning with the same event
items.description: Shows a breakdown of where unique users came from when visiting your app.

items.name: Daily Active Users (DAUs) 123
items.description: Shows the number of unique users that use your app every day.

items.name: Sample - Purchase conversion funnel
items.description: This is a sample of how a user funnel could look like. It represents the number of users that performed a specific action at each step.
